cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CV 

This paper discusses recent advances and challenges in Federated Learning, which is a subfield of Machine Learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper also discusses privacy risks and costs, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper may also be relevant to researchers in the fields of Distributed Computing (cs.DC), Signal Processing (cs.SI), and Computer Vision (cs.CV) due to the decentralized nature of Federated Learning.
